title: Equipment for the production of polyethylene bags and printing machine US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000
title_uz: Polietilen paket ishlab chiqarish va ustki qismiga yozuv bosish uskunasi US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000
title_ru: Оборудование для производства полиэтиленовых пакетов и печати сверху US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000
title_en: Equipment for the production of polyethylene bags and printing machine US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000
short_description: This US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000 model equipment also produces pockets and serves to print various inscriptions and patterns on the upper part. It has a production capacity of up to 70 kg per hour, a total power of 45 kW and a weight of 6200 kg. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and their prices differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000 modeldagi uskuna ham paket ishlab chiqaradi va ustki qismiga har xil yozuv va naqshlani bosish uchun ham xizmat qiladi. Soatiga 70 kg gacha mahsulot ishlab chiqarish quvvatiga ega, umumiy quvvati 45 kW va vazni 6200 kg ni tashkil qiladi. Tavsifda ushbu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham mavjud va ularning narxlari bir-biridan farq qiladi.
short_description_ru: Данное оборудование модели US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000 также производит пакеты и служит для нанесения на верхнюю часть различных надписей и рисунков. Имеет производственную мощность до 70 кг в час, общую мощность 45 кВт и вес 6200 кг. В описании есть и другие модели данного оборудования, и их цены отличаются друг от друга.

long_description:
This US-SJ-60-1000ASY-1000 model equipment also produces pockets and serves to print various inscriptions and patterns on the upper part. It has a production capacity of up to 70 kg per hour, a total power of 45 kW and a weight of 6200 kg. There are other models of this equipment in the description, and their prices differ from each other.
